										class data
										{
											singleType="STRING";
											value="Several weeks ago, General Duarte Pereira led a military coup against the elected government of Isla Pera and declared himself the country's leader.<br/><br/>" \n "" \n "Since seizing power, Pereira's regime has carried out purges and war crimes against political opponents, while launching aggressive operations against neighboring islands.<br/><br/>" \n "" \n "These actions have drawn international condemnation, and NATO forces have been authorized to intervene. Elements of the USMC and US Navy have arrived in the region to conduct a rapid strike against the junta.<br/><br/>" \n "" \n "Your unit will spearhead the operation by striking key military targets and destabilizing the regime's control over the island.";
